I ran into the same issue when I rolled our IT infrastructure for 
another startup I am doing!
The EC2 reserved is the best long term value, and it is much faster. 
Hopefully, I will be selling many more of these as well going forward. 
The cool thing is that Amazon lowers the price and passes the savings 
directly to us when they figure out ways to save $$$$.

